heading: Diablo IV Patch 2.0.2 Patch Notes
content: Blizzard released the 2.0.2 Patch Notes right after the Vessel of Hatred Pre-Launch Livestream! Legendary aspect affix values now have a separate cap between Ancestral and Non-Ancestral items. Now, the maximum values for aspects can only be found on Ancestral items.
